OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry day with some good
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine, though more cloud
OL,7,Fat times around Mull and Oban, and
OL,8,Fhigh cloud increasing elsewhere later.
OL,9,FVery warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA very warm and sunny evening
OL,12,Fwill be followed by a dry night with
OL,13,Fsome clear spells though sea fog may
OL,14,Fdrift in towards the Argyll Islands.
OL,15,FWinds remaining light.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FAnother dry day with some good
OL,18,Fspells of sunshine, though there could
OL,19,Fbe some mist and sea fog around the
OL,20,FArgyll Islands for a time. A hot day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
