OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fcooler cloudier Saturday with best of
OL,7,Fsun on west coast. Cloudy start on
OL,8,FSunday then brightening up with sunny
OL,9,Fintervals. Monday dry and sunny and
OL,10,Fbecoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
